<br>
We aren't starting on a level playing field either.  What you call competition is anything but.  A European uberguild will always beat out a Japanese uberguild will always beat out an American east-coast uberguild will always beat out an American west-coast uberguild will always beat out a family-oriented uberguild of working professionals.  That last one is essentially what TK is.  Despite having over a hundred level 60's without ever recruiting and more combined clerics, rogues, warriors and wizards than any guild on the server, CiH included, we will never allow ourselves to fall into the trap of ruining the game for other people.  On the very rare occasion where we've done exactly that we've felt terrible about it.<br>
<br>
If you'd like to continue the debate I'm all for it.<br>
